{"tid":2376940,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點解喝茶可以成日反面合體之後體反面再合體","createTime":"2021-01-23T07:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T10:07:52.000Z","uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25ba8143b1800cd2f22d047b1ad2184cdc4a3953","tid":2376940,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"2007年出道<br />\n<br />\n2014年拆夥<br />\n<br />\n2018年 <br />\nHotCha成立11周年，合體舉辦十周年慈善演唱會。3位成員於演唱會前接受訪問時表示過去真的經常嗌交，但現在成員間都懂得互相欣賞，友情和默契仍在<br />\n<br />\n2020年<br />\n《Chill Club》邀請今年成軍13周年的組合HotCha作嘉賓，這次是成員張紋嘉（Crystal）、張惠雅（Regen）及黎美言（Winkie）繼兩年前演唱會後再度合體。<br />\n<br />\n2021年<br />\n張惠雅與舊拍檔張紋嘉撇清關係<br />\n張惠雅還很介意有傳媒向她的舊隊友Crystal（張紋嘉）了解，Regen昨日指自己收到對方1個Message，但其實二人之間一直沒有聯絡，亦沒有問候對方：「大家都安好，大家都唔好再問我或者佢，I am so sick of this（我很討厭這樣）！」<br />\n<br />\n2022年<br />\nHotcha成軍15周年合體舉辦十五周年紅館演唱會"},{"pid":"42eb724e8619f3199abb5b8bebdecb90d0e68ab4","tid":2376940,"uid":104210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"甜酸苦也都好！"},{"pid":"acadb2c72a377cc3cc90a7e53825c30c58510e59","tid":2376940,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"小動作 <br />\n來叫我混亂又快樂"},{"pid":"0d9ddc5f595bd854e50d3fc1807a09fa71b40089","tid":2376940,"uid":228793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"洗哂d錢咪夾band"},{"pid":"8b122023ffa1f3c1159772d4034aa154f6edb6bf","tid":2376940,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"Beyond咪又係咁"},{"pid":"07d88b1a0eb874ef3281f5f0f105a45f4affedd1","tid":2376940,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"oasis都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34327cb6d5c0f6564e33b9e0aa867adcc054b944","tid":2376940,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"洗曬d錢咪合體<img src=